author: kfogel
msg: Fix typos in the svntest system.
(APR_REPO): Use correct spelling of self, instead of "ARP_REPO".
This typo wouldn't affect anything in normal usage, but it could
have bitten someone who used an unusual configuration.

author: rooneg
msg: Fix svn_ra_replay over DAV when the send_deltas parameter is FALSE.
(start_element): Call maybe_close_file in the add/open file and add/open
directory cases, to potentially clean up the last opened file.
(end_element): Call maybe_close_file in the editor_report case to close
the last file, and stop closing files in apply_textdelta's case since it
is not going to be hit in the send_deltas == FALSE case.
